## Testing / Ops Notes

- **Replica set:** `MeritTransferService.create` uses multi-document transactions; integration tests should use **`MongoMemoryReplSet`** (not a standalone `MongoMemoryServer`), see `api/apps/meriter/test/merit-transfer.service.spec.ts`.
- **Wipe / seed:** include `merit_transfers` in destructive maintenance the same way as other domain collections (see `platform-wipe.service.ts` if extended).

